  "lyrics": [
    {
      "t": 4800,
      "text": "I hear the train a-coming'",
      "end": 7680
    },
    {
      "t": 7680,
      "text": "It's rolling around the bend",
      "end": 10040
    },
    {
      "t": 10040,
      "text": "And I ain't seen the sunshine since",
      "end": 12990
    },
    {
      "t": 12990,
      "text": "I don't know when",
      "end": 15240
    },
    {
      "t": 15240,
      "text": "I'm stuck in Folsom prison",
      "end": 17890
    },
    {
      "t": 17890,
      "text": "And time keeps dragging on",
      "end": 21110
    },
    {
      "t": 21110,
      "text": "But that train keeps a-rollin'",
      "end": 27660
    },
    {
      "t": 27660,
      "text": "On down to San Antone",
      "end": 31560
    },
    {
      "t": 31560,
      "text": "When I was just a baby",
      "end": 34360
    },
    {
      "t": 34360,
      "text": "My mama told me, \"son",
      "end": 36830
    },
    {
      "t": 36830,
      "text": "Always be a good boy",
      "end": 39250
    },
    {
      "t": 39250,
      "text": "Don't ever play with guns\"",
      "end": 41940
    },
    {
      "t": 41940,
      "text": "But I shot a man in Reno",
      "end": 44620
    },
    {
      "t": 44620,
      "text": "Just to watch him die",
      "end": 47740
    },
    {
      "t": 47740,
      "text": "When I hear that whistle blowin'",
      "end": 53510
    },
    {
      "t": 53510,
      "text": "I hang my head and cry",
      "end": 80700
    },
    {
      "t": 80700,
      "text": "I bet there's rich folks eatin'",
      "end": 86420
    },
    {
      "t": 86420,
      "text": "In a fancy dinin' car",
      "end": 88720
    },
    {
      "t": 88720,
      "text": "They're probably drinkin' coffee",
      "end": 91030
    },
    {
      "t": 91030,
      "text": "And smokin' big cigars",
      "end": 93390
    },
    {
      "t": 93390,
      "text": "Well, I know I had it comin'",
      "end": 95580
    },
    {
      "t": 95580,
      "text": "I know I can't be free",
      "end": 99070
    },
    {
      "t": 99070,
      "text": "But those people keep a-movin'",
      "end": 105150
    },
    {
      "t": 105150,
      "text": "And that's what tortures me",
      "end": 130100
    },
    {
      "t": 130100,
      "text": "Well, if they freed me from this prison",
      "end": 137630
    },
    {
      "t": 137630,
      "text": "If that railroad train was mine",
      "end": 139950
    },
    {
      "t": 139950,
      "text": "Bet I'd move it on a little",
      "end": 142360
    },
    {
      "t": 142360,
      "text": "Farther down the line",
      "end": 145300
    },
    {
      "t": 145300,
      "text": "Far from Folsom Prison",
      "end": 147590
    },
    {
      "t": 147590,
      "text": "That's where I want to stay",
      "end": 150400
    },
    {
      "t": 150400,
      "text": "And I'd let that lonesome whistle",
      "end": 156790
    },
    {
      "t": 156790,
      "text": "Blow my blues away"
    }
  ],
